drop table "SYS_User" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "SYS_User" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "SYS_User"
(
"UserID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"REMUserId" VARCHAR2(50),
"UserAccount" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"UserNumber" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"UserPwd" VARCHAR2(50) not null,
"UserName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"Age" INTEGER,
"Email" VARCHAR2(100) not null,
"Phone" NVARCHAR2(50),
"Mobile" NVARCHAR2(50),
"SourceFrom" INTEGER default 1,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_SYS_USER primary key ("UserID")
);

comment on table "SYS_User" is
'用户表';

comment on column "SYS_User"."SourceFrom" is
'1: 来自老REM系统
0: 来自可视化系统';

comment on column "SYS_User"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';
